Package: vec
Architecture: any
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}, libsqlite3-0
Recommends: vec-model-base
Description: Semantic file search — find files by meaning
 locate finds files by name. vec finds files by meaning.
 .
 vec indexes the filesystem with CPU-based embeddings (pure-Rust ONNX, no
 Python, no cloud, no external service), stores only vectors and byte
 offsets in a central SQLite database, and enforces per-user access control
 via filesystem permissions.
 .
 After 'apt install vec vec-model-base', open a terminal and type
 'vec "authentication middleware"' — it works with no manual setup.

Package: vec-model-base
Architecture: all
Depends: ${misc:Depends}
Description: Embedding model for vec (gte-multilingual-base, 50+ languages)
 gte-multilingual-base ONNX embedding model and tokenizer for vec.
 .
 Supports 50+ languages, ~90 MB. Versioned independently from the vec
 binary. After upgrading this package, run 'vec updatedb --full' to
 re-embed with the new model weights.
